data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN WITH INTEREST RATE OF 3.125%!! Welcome home to this beautiful 40 acre ranchette! You will fall in love with this custom built, energy efficient, stucco home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Enjoy your wrap around covered porch all year long! Step inside to the grand foyer. You will love the tall vaulted ceilings and large rooms. The kitchen is open to the dining room with a large island, great for entertaining! If you have ever wanted a large pantry, look no further! The living room right off the kitchen is nice and cozy, great for movie nights! The large master bedroom is complete with a large master bathroom, walk in shower and access to the covered patio. The second bedroom is also quite large with tons of natural light! The laundry room/ mud room is on the main level as well. Upstairs you will find a loft with an attached non conforming bedroom! Great place for the kids to hang out, extra space for guests or storage! The property features a shed/barn with one stall and corral for horses or livestock, storage shed, chicken coop, and a newer arena with a roping chute. The property is fully fenced. Also, it is located close to amenities, the property is 15 minutes away from Otis, CO and 20 minutes away from Akron, CO. This property is also handicap accessible. Come and enjoy the quiet country life!
